data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. MOTIVATED SELLER! BRING ALL OFFERS!!!NEW CARPET in living area downstairs!! Spacious 5 bedroom 3.5 bath home located in Tavares, "America's Sea Plane City". The home backs up to a conservation area. The open floor plan  offers plenty of space to entertain family and friends for all occasions.  Flex Room provides the perfect opportunity for a home office, formal dining and/or sitting room. The Master Suite is located downstairs just off the living room. Upstairs you will find 4 additional bedrooms, one being a junior suite, third full bathroom and laundry room. BONUS ROOM ALERT!!! The loft area is a HUGE win for game night and movie marathons for the whole family! DON'T MISS THIS ONE! There is a water softener system with the house and a new hot water heater and new Bosch dishwasher. VACANT!!! EASY TO SHOW!!
